# radroots-events-codec-wasm

Wasm bindings for Rad Roots event encoding and decoding.

## Goals

- expose Rad Roots event codec functions to wasm targets with stable interfaces
- preserve deterministic tag generation and JSON conversion behavior in wasm
- keep binding APIs aligned with core codec rules across SDK surfaces
- provide a reliable bridge layer for JavaScript and browser integrations

